{
  "stem": "15721.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the second tallest fellow, biggest fellow in the class, was a leader in the Hitler Youth movement and he heard that statement.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He grabbed a hold of my neck, turned me around, and said, I heard what you said.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You have exactly 10 seconds to apologize or else I'll go to the Gestapo, the secret police.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he pulled out-- he had a little, you know, grandfather watch with an open cover and he propped it open.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the-- the teacher stood there, the professor stood there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was totally powerless, he couldn't intervene.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when the 10 seconds were over, I said to him, I know who said it, but I won't tell you.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he closed the-- the watch, put it back in his watch pocket, and then hauled off to floor me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Well, my father have been very foresighted and had engaged a retired police captain to teach me jujitsu.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was very much prepared for that kind of an attack and the next moment this fellow lay on the floor.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was in high school for two more years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was never touched.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was the only Jew left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was another Jew in my class and he was beaten up so regularly that his parents took him to Switzerland to finish school.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I was never touched, not-- not once.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In fact, even when they had their-- their dance for graduation in May of-- April, 1935, they invited me to come with a Jewish girl, of course, it's the only one I would date anyhow.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I decided that I would make an appearance and for about eight, 10 minutes the two of us were there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We once danced one dance and then we left because it was uncomfortable.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
